emails.subject: RE: NOPA Crush Data on Platform?
emails.body_text:
Hi Oscar,

 

I wanted to follow up on my previous message regarding the historical NOPA Soybean Crush data.

I apologize for the earlier incorrect information. 

 

To clarify, we do indeed have access to the data. 

 

However, NOPA has an exclusive distribution agreement with Reuters, which means we can use the data for our internal analysis but unfortunately cannot share it externally.

I appreciate your understanding and apologize again for any confusion caused.

 

Best regards,

Saber Khalfallah
